Patch 8.0.0048
Problem:    On Windows job_stop() stops cmd.exe, not the processes it runs.
            (Linwei)
Solution:   Iterate over all processes and terminate the one where the parent
            is the job process. (Yasuhiro Matsumoto, closes #1184)
